ile.com/diamond-details/29262051?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational">2.00ct Cushion Modified</a></td><td>GIA</td><td>E / VVS1</td><td>Ideal</td><td><strong>$22,438</strong></td><td>9 reviews</td></tr></tbody></table>

