**Natural 2ct colour guidance:** G colour in a cushion modified brilliant at 2ct is borderline. In platinum or white gold, G may show slight warmth in the body of a large cushion at 2ct face-up. In yellow gold, G is ideal — the warm metal reflection absorbs any body colour. For white metal settings at 2ct, F colour or above is the correct choice.

